transcripts: In Auto virtual wall creates an invisible barrier that Roomba won't cross start by inserting the batteries. You can set a virtual wall to block openings have up to seven feet, for best performance point the arrows on top of the virtual wall towards the opening you want to block place a virtual wall on the outside of the door way you want to block.
